lyrics:
Lord prepare me; to be a sanctuary;
Pure and holy; tried and true;
With thanksgiving,
I'll be a living Sanctuary for You.

If I'm holy, As you are holy
Then I'll see You - face to face;
Melt and mould me, - In Your image;
Take me to, - Your holy place.

Lead me on Lord, - From temptation,
Purify me, - from within;
Fill my heart with, - Your Holy Spirit;
Taking away, - all my sins.

For it is You Lord -Who came to save me,
The heart and soul- Of, every man
For it is You Lord -Who know my weakness
And give strength with;
Thine own hands
